 terme leur projet d’étude. Oui, le doctorat peut être une aventure passionnante !  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aDissertations, AcademicvHandbooks, manuals, etc. 0aDoctor of philosophy degree. 0aDoctoral studentsxPsychology. 0aDoctoral studentsxSocial conditions. 0aResearchxMethodology. 7aEDUCATION / Higher.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311127268908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2023z978311127195808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2019z978311127498040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9782763742977?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763742977423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763742977/original  a978-3-11-127195-8  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2023b2023  a978-3-11-127268-9  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  a978-3-11-127498-0  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2019b2019  aGBV-deGruyter-alles